data.description: Welcome to this exquisite residence boasting three spacious bedrooms and two luxurious full baths. Take advantage of the $10,000 Philly First Grant, plus an additional $10,000 boost program from Prosperity Home Mortgage.  This grant can be used for Closing Costs, Buy Rate Down, additional down payment, etc. Grant is 100% forgivable and you dont have to be a 1rst time home buyer to be able to use this money. Feel free to reach out for more information. This property comes with a 1-year home warranty for your peace of mind.  Nestled on a serene block in the desirable Tacony neighborhood, this property offers a prime location with convenient access to the 95 highway. As you step inside, a charming porch welcomes you, and your eyes are immediately drawn to the stunning luxury vinyl flooring that graces the entire home. The formal dining room seamlessly connects to the stylish kitchen island, which doubles as a delightful breakfast bar. Continuing through the kitchen, you'll discover a generous-sized patio featuring both a tile section and an elegant wood platform, perfect for relaxing or entertaining. Upstairs, three generously proportioned bedrooms await you, each adorned with tasteful updates and accompanied by a beautiful bathroom showcasing a timeless design with white and gray tiles.  The lower level offers a fully finished basement, complete with a full bathroom, currently utilized as a captivating movie room complemented by a convenient bar area. Don't miss out on the opportunity to experience this remarkable property firsthand—schedule your appointment today. Showings are effortless and convenient.
